  "body": "Hey, it's Zeno Rocha.\r\n\r\nWe just finished ourВ 6th launch week https://resend.com/launch-weeks/6, and it's been one of our most packed releases so far.\r\n\r\n----------------------------------------\r\n\r\nQ: We're planning our next major features. What would you like us to ship next?\r\n(We read every email)\r\n\r\n----------------------------------------\r\n\r\nHere's a quick recap of everything we launched:\r\n\r\n * Day 1: Automations https://resend.com/blog/introducing-automations\r\n\r\n * Day 2: AI Email Editor https://resend.com/blog/ai-email-editor\r\n\r\n * Day 3: Resend CLI 2.0 https://resend.com/blog/resend-cli-2\r\n\r\n * Day 4: Custom Tracking Domains https://resend.com/blog/introducing-custom-tracking-domain\r\n\r\n * Day 5: React Email 6.0 https://resend.com/blog/react-email-6\r\n\r\n * Day 6: Resend Forward https://resend.com/blog/resend-forward\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://youtu.be/S2iS1xZ12Ns\r\n\r\nNow, let's cover each individual launch in detail.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nDAY 1: AUTOMATIONS\r\n\r\nhttps://resend.com/blog/introducing-automations\r\n\r\nOn Monday, we launched Automations, a new way to orchestrate lifecycle emails triggered by events in your app.\r\n\r\nWith Automations, you can:\r\n\r\n * Define a triggerВ from an event in your app\r\n\r\n * Personalize each stepВ with delays, waits, and conditions\r\n\r\n * Get full visibilityВ into every run in real time\r\n\r\nв†’ Read the announcement https://resend.com/blog/introducing-automations\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nDAY 2: AI EMAIL EDITOR\r\n\r\nhttps://resend.com/blog/ai-email-editor\r\n\r\nOn Tuesday, we announced the new Resend email editor, extended by AI.\r\n\r\nThe editor helps you:\r\n\r\n * Start with your existing contentВ by turning a URL into an on-brand draft\r\n\r\n * Bring your own agentic stackВ via the Resend MCP server\r\n\r\n * Catch mistakesВ before you hit send\r\n\r\nв†’ Read the announcement https://resend.com/blog/ai-email-editor\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nDAY 3: RESEND CLI 2.0\r\n\r\nhttps://resend.com/blog/resend-cli-2\r\n\r\nOn Wednesday, we shipped version 2.0 of the Resend CLI with powerful new features:\r\n\r\n * Send emails using local React files\r\n\r\n * Manage Automations and eventsВ from your terminal\r\n\r\n * Skills for AI agentsВ to interact with the Resend API\r\n\r\nThe CLI now gives you access to 50+ commands across the full Resend API, without leaving your terminal.\r\n\r\nв†’ Read the announcement https://resend.com/blog/resend-cli-2\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nDAY 4: CUSTOM TRACKING DOMAINS\r\n\r\nhttps://resend.com/blog/introducing-custom-tracking-domain\r\n\r\nOn Thursday, we launched custom tracking domains, free for all Resend users.\r\n\r\nTracking through a domain you own:\r\n\r\n * Keeps your sender reputation isolated from shared infrastructure\r\n\r\n * Aligns with your sending domain for better deliverability\r\n\r\n * Shows your recipients a familiar domain on every link\r\n\r\nIt works for bothВ click trackingВ andВ open tracking, and can be configured through the Dashboard or the API.\r\n\r\nв†’ Read the announcement https://resend.com/blog/introducing-custom-tracking-domain\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nDAY 5: REACT EMAIL 6.0\r\n\r\nhttps://resend.com/blog/react-email-6\r\n\r\nOn Friday, we announced a new major version ofВ react.email https://react.email/, featuring a new open-source email editor you can embed directly in your own app.\r\n\r\nReact Email 6 includes:\r\n\r\n * An embeddable editorВ that you can drop into your app with one line of code\r\n\r\n * New templatesВ for authentication and e-commerce flows\r\n\r\n * Unified packageВ for easier integration\r\n\r\nв†’ Read the announcement https://resend.com/blog/react-email-6\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nDAY 6: RESEND FORWARD\r\n\r\nhttps://resend.com/blog/resend-forward\r\n\r\nOn Saturday, we announcedВ Resend Forward https://resend.com/forward, our first-ever conference. By builders, for builders.\r\n\r\nJoin us in San Francisco on October 21st for a full day focused on the craft behind building software. We'll hear from leaders working at the edge of software and AI, with a special emphasis on practical tools and ideas you can actually use.\r\n\r\nв†’ Join the waitlist https://resend.com/forward\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nHappy sending,\r\nZeno Rocha\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n----------------------------------------\r\n\r\nYou are receiving this email because you opted in via our site.\r\n\r\nWant to change how you receive these emails?\r\nYou can unsubscribe from this list https://unsubscribe.resend.com/?token=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJjb250YWN0SWQiOiI2Y2U2YWU2Mi0zNzI5LTQ3ZTUtYTI2MC1jODgxZTI4YmY2ZmUiLCJhdWRpZW5jZUlkIjpudWxsLCJicm9hZGNhc3RJZCI6Ijk2YjQxMDg3LWQyNTMtNDc0OS1iOTU3LTE5Mjg4N2QyMjVmMiIsInRlYW1JZCI6IjQwYjQ4YzA5LTFiZjEtNGQ2Mi1hZjI5LTdjMTYxM2QyZWQ3NSIsImV4cCI6MTgwODU1NTAxNn0.Uc8MMoaxb_nNkMi7B-uy8ygDySlgc7DVQXRUNF8lVWI.\r\n\r\n2261 Market Street #5039\r\nSan Francisco, CA 94114\r\n\r\n\r\n",
